{"tid":406643,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[新手貓奴] 主子每晚狂抓狂叫","createTime":"2017-09-19T22:12:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T10:40:10.000Z","uid":46457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ff5030d68f7c0d1335daf00cadee642ef9206f31","tid":406643,"uid":46457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T22:12:20.000Z","msg":"剛有主子入屋頭幾天，屋企有d 地方裝修唔想佢去到因為有危險，咁夜晚比佢入返籠，佢就狂大聲叫同抓砂玩屎搞到成個籠d 野反晒d 砂撥晒出黎，我就訓係隔離，佢玩到我面都有砂 飛砂到九丈遠<br />\n<br />\n想請教有咩含意同有冇對策呢，加紙皮係籠內擋住墊住是否可行之策"},{"pid":"d56f90fed531f6547811e4358348ed2adc0c98ba","tid":406643,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T22:21:55.000Z","msg":"頭幾日係咁㗎啦，忍耐吓啦"},{"pid":"7203d69f35373e0843eab7cab4a36bc6e4996a85","tid":406643,"uid":46457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T23:22:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頭幾日係咁㗎啦，忍耐吓啦</blockquote><br />\n我係咪唔可以理佢<br />\n有時佢叫到好攰我就放佢出黎"},{"pid":"00457ce602d6beb532fea8875df470b08df67a31","tid":406643,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T00:15:59.000Z","msg":"我隻貓都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n發覺只要佢見唔到人自己再嗌一陣就會停<br />\n但到6點幾又會狂叫 因為肚餓"},{"pid":"2b223b685523fd4f11cb8123a062f0b191a5aac1","tid":406643,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T00:18:53.000Z","msg":"唔好理佢，可以既拎走個盤<br />\n佢仲細？"},{"pid":"a9785401e7f14146c7401397f33e98208500b87a","tid":406643,"uid":69168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T00:20:55.000Z","msg":"絕咗育未？"},{"pid":"8d6b819eb3103c33509ad4ad83ca1ac67e3a6dbd","tid":406643,"uid":10640,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T00:23:36.000Z","msg":"D貓撚真係on9，主你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe0a5aa30484a4be2533ff79b090e0aad6fe75d","tid":406643,"uid":20396,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"r