"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1a789ca2ad2b9442fea9027e65bfff95773898","tid":406643,"uid":52227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T03:29:16.000Z","msg":"點解佢屙左屎你訓係隔離都頂得順唔剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d433dcaeae0933a7a9e4b37308fd8896b8502487","tid":406643,"uid":46457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T04:26:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解佢屙左屎你訓係隔離都頂得順唔剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n半夜訓緊點睇佢有冇屙屎，我係屋企個陣已經有屎即剷"},{"pid":"a65d0de8e405970a87b0e4210c44b310b50949f5","tid":406643,"uid":28619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T04:47:55.000Z","msg":"試下放入廁所關門<br />\n廁所活動範圍大過籠，會舒服啲"},{"pid":"37ad782a13637f1fffabc49d2805638ad0c15095","tid":406643,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T04:49:53.000Z","msg":"我主人養左11年 每晚都係狂叫 好撚情緒激動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3503a89606f8e7e72d66554e2ba171f98cb010","tid":406643,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T04:57:31.000Z","msg":"逼佢屙完屎尿先扔佢入籠，收走個砂盤<br />\n大約4-5個鐘係監視底下放風，食野飲水屙屎尿再困過（如有需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"e9955a16eaf7957887ba000d0d7bab307818bf51","tid":406643,"uid":35095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T05:31:52.000Z","msg":"因為貓貓唔鍾意困籠呀<br />\n幾時先可以唔洗困？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f1c28cf5be537b98841ebcc1e0f52e60c3a2e4","tid":406643,"uid":46457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T06:11:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我主人養左11年 每晚都係狂叫 好撚情緒激動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你點解決<br />\n<br />\n我樓上既方法逐個試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢黎先兩日，困一星期到自然會放行<br />\n同埋主要想train 佢入籠都乖乖地，知道我地屋企人係到陪住佢，唔會叫到咁淒慘"},{"pid":"a6cb9285630a43333c905b8880ad52047e158e98","tid":406643,"uid":45684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T06:17:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我主人養左11年 每晚都係狂叫 好撚情緒激動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你點解決<br />\n<br />\n我樓上既方法逐個試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢黎先兩日，困一星期到自然會放行<br />\n同埋主要想train 佢入籠都乖乖地，知道我地屋企人係到陪住佢，唔會叫到咁淒慘</blockquote><br />\n裝修完會比佢全日通屋走?<br />\n調返轉, 我隻貓係train到佢知困入籠=罰佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ecdd8257f8caf72d82d2849715e80ec24b3c5d2","tid":406643,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T06:23:38.000Z","msg":"養得耐<br />\n<br />\n就可以完全唔用籠"},{"pid":"71dc97d1f3a2b5708550ee904def1a23ea50f5f7","tid":406643,"uid":46457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T06:27:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我主人養左11年 每晚都係狂叫 好撚情緒激動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你點解決<br />\n<br />\n我樓上既方法逐個試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢黎先兩日，困一星期到自然會放行<br />\n同埋主要想train 佢入籠都乖乖地，知道我地屋企人係到陪住佢，唔會叫到咁淒慘</blockquote><br />\n裝修完會比佢全日通屋走?<br />\n調返轉, 我隻貓係train到佢知困入籠=罰佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最理想係咁<br />\n<br />\n但你岩岩養個陣有冇困籠，你貓嘈唔嘈先<br />\n我個隻唔入籠都好多野講，困籠嘈到驚隔離屋以為我虐畜"},{"pid":"8f2be06b7dc3f866b920a07a5ef54a17d58d27e4","tid":406643,"uid":52227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T10:40:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解佢屙左屎你訓係隔離都頂得順唔剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n半夜訓緊點睇佢有冇屙屎，我係屋企個陣已經有屎即剷</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我次次都聞到屎味就會醒所以我先問，明明我啲朋友都話佢啲臭無乜味"}]}